Big Brother Naija housemate, Nengi on Thursday was issued a fine by Biggie. Nengi was issued a fine for microphone/audio infringement. The BBNaija female housemate was whispering to Ozo. Whispering and having secret codes is against the rules of BBNaija season 5 reality show. Biggie announced that the fine will attract a deduction from her wallet. This is the first time Nengi will be issued a fine for microphone infringement.